Package: windkanal
Title: Simulation Testbed for Living Clinical Data Systems
Version: 0.2.1
Authors@R:
    person("Christian", "Obeser", email = "gersari99@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A wind tunnel for living clinical data systems: simulates
    growing routine-care data streams (session-wise outcomes, patients
    nested in therapists, staggered patient entry) so that estimators
    (e.g. heterogeneous treatment effect methods) and analysis
    governance protocols (continuous peeking vs. release gates) can be
    stress-tested against known ground truth before touching real
    clinical data. Settings are configurable; calibrated presets and a
    plasmode mode are planned.
